      <title>卡尼总理说，特朗普想破坏加拿大。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-24/trump-wants-to-break-canada-carney-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）说，美国将永远不会拥有加拿大。卡尼在3月23日说：“唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）希望打破我们，以便美国能够拥有我们。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-24/trump-wants-to-break-canada-carney-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:26:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国工厂活动滑入收缩领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-24/us-factory-activity-slides-into-contraction-territory-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于S＆amp; P Global Flash March工厂指数从2022年中期以来的最高水平下降了近3点至49.8点，因此美国的制造业本月退回了收缩领域。服务活动量规攀升至三个月高，Flash March Composite指数增加了3分，达到52.4。马特·米勒（Matt Miller）和丹尼·汉堡（Dani Burger）有有关彭博电视台的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-24/us-factory-activity-slides-into-contraction-territory-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总统说，刚果可能会扩大钴出口悬挂。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/congo-may-extend-cobalt-export-suspension-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费利克斯·托斯塞克迪（Felix Tshisekedi）总统说，刚果民主共和国可能会将钴出口的暂停超过计划的四个月，因为它考虑了维持电动车电池材料价格更高价格的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/congo-may-extend-cobalt-export-suspension-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 13:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bullion Explorer用新名称制作Maga Pitch：在美国制造黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/canadian-firm-tsxv-pali-changes-subsidiary-name-to-made-in-america-gold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家加拿大投资公司将其注重美国的子公司的名称更改为NV King Goldlands制造的America Gold。随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）鼓励企业将业务搬迁到该国，并威胁要升级的关税进口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/canadian-firm-tsxv-pali-changes-subsidiary-name-to-made-in-america-gold</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 12:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着市场的增长，印度简化全球资金的披露规范</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/india-eases-disclosure-norm-for-global-funds-on-market-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的证券市场监管机构周一批准提高规则实施后不到两年的全球基金的最终奖励所有权的颗粒状披露的门槛，原因是该国股票市场交易的股票数量增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/india-eases-disclosure-norm-for-global-funds-on-market-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 12:03:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在与美国官员会面时寻求关税缓刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-officials-to-visit-india-this-week-as-tariff-deadline-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士说，当美国官员周二到达该国关于双边贸易协定的会谈时，印度政府将寻求免除唐纳德·特朗普总统的互惠关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-officials-to-visit-india-this-week-as-tariff-deadline-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 09:15:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债落在迹象表明特朗普将稀释四月关税的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-treasuries-fall-on-signs-that-trump-will-dilute-april-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债下跌，这表明投资者赞成风险更大的资产，此前有报道称唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的总统宣布下个月将比他所指出的更具针对性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-treasuries-fall-on-signs-that-trump-will-dilute-april-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 09:14:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
