      <title>当土耳其官员试图加强防御力时，里拉受到了压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/turkish-lira-offshore-cost-default-swaps-hold-near-recent-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其当局介入稳定市场后，总统雷切普·泰耶普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）最有权势的对手拘留了对该国政策道路的巨大抛售和信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/turkish-lira-offshore-cost-default-swaps-hold-near-recent-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 05:22:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券的关税标志：市场包裹，股票提升技术提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/asian-stocks-under-pressure-as-uncertainty-rises-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当贸易商抢购了受虐的科技股时，股票在本周开始，并表明唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税将比预期减少的安全性更大。债券倒下了。美元和金色几乎没有发芽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/asian-stocks-under-pressure-as-uncertainty-rises-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:28:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
